## ðŸ”§ Archivos a Copiar/Crear

### Backend - ACTUALIZAR

**Archivo:** `isrc-spotify-backend/package.json`

Reemplaza la secciÃ³n `"scripts"`:

```json
"scripts": {
  "start": "node server.js",
  "dev": "nodemon server.js"
},
```

### Backend - NUEVO

Crea archivo: `isrc-spotify-backend/vercel.json`

```json
{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "server.js",
      "use": "@vercel/node"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "server.js"
    }
  ],
  "env": {
    "NODE_ENV": "production"
  }
}
```

---

### Frontend - NUEVO

Crea archivo: `isrc-spotify-frontend/package.json`

```json
{
  "name": "isrc-spotify-frontend",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "dependencies": {
    "react": "^18.2.0",
    "react-dom": "^18.2.0",
    "react-scripts": "5.0.1",
    "axios": "^1.6.0",
    "web-vitals": "^2.1.4"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "start": "react-scripts start",
    "build": "react-scripts build",
    "test": "react-scripts test",
    "eject": "react-scripts eject"
  },
  "eslintConfig": {
    "extends": [
      "react-app"
    ]
  },
  "browserslist": {
    "production": [
      ">0.2%",
      "not dead",
      "not op_mini all"
    ],
    "development": [
      "last 1 chrome version",
      "last 1 firefox version",
      "last 1 safari version"
    ]
  }
}
```

### Frontend - NUEVO

Crea archivo: `isrc-spotify-frontend/index.jsx`

```jsx
